{"tid":758636,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恒生發威 市值跑贏支銀","createTime":"2018-07-28T01:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T03:42:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"018b652b0b7cb7d2adaa31e3230491ed30d79235","tid":758636,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T01:41:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180728/58495483\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F58495483&d=6BTf8xs85qiJDV7eXNNnQwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=35e7f78b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180728%2F58495483&h=911b6beb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180728/58495483</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180727/large/1532703584_cac1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180727%2Flarge%2F1532703584_cac1.jpg&h=9729bb52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港股昨微升23點，恒生銀行（011）股價繼續發威，升1.25%，至210.2元，尾市創下210.6元的歷史新高，成交2.67億元。恒生股價節節上升的同時，中銀香港（2388）近期表現卻浮浮沉沉，昨收市升0.26%，報37.9元，跑輸恒生。恒生市值4,018億元，超過了中銀香港的4,007億元。於2016年初，恒生市值較中銀香港為高，中銀香港及後展開較強升勢，市值超越恒生，現時再被恒生反超前。記者：黃尹華<br />\n<br />\n宏滙資產管理董事及投資策略總監林嘉麒表示，本地銀行股近日明顯有資金流入，反映市場預期本地銀行會受未來美國加息及息差擴闊前景利好。因本地銀行大多持有美元資產，美元強勢和人民幣跌勢令資金更願意買入美元資產，預計未來再有資金流入及破頂機會高。"},{"pid":"31a4022254abdfac7dccae47a99a3b3dd685618e","tid":758636,"uid":48334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:12:16.000Z","msg":"升到咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af03021f56d69180a9dbe625a3117a1cb3fd17b","tid":758636,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:17:34.000Z","msg":"香港人的銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3fec407680b12dde2d4e137e9c7b9e465b5417","tid":758636,"uid":63017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6af03021f56d69180a9dbe625a3117a1cb3fd17b","tid":758636,"uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T02:17:34.000Z","msg":"香港人的銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:42:27.000Z","msg":"已經比大笨象收購<br />\n大新先港資"}]}